{
  "id": "699a747d7eb9479b38d0875c",
  "title": "tagがついたページをfetchしたい",
  "created": 1771730046,
  "updated": 1771934335,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "699a747d7eb9479b38d0875c",
      "text": "tagがついたページをfetchしたい",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730046,
      "updated": 1771730046
    },
    {
      "id": "699a747e000000000022143e",
      "text": "　ページ内に #tag というページを全て取得したい",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730046,
      "updated": 1771730046
    },
    {
      "id": "699a747e000000000022143f",
      "text": "　\tAPI経由で可能？",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730046,
      "updated": 1771730046
    },
    {
      "id": "699a748c00000000005a271d",
      "text": " リンク記法と見分けて、`#`のtagで書かれたページ名だけを取得したいとき",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730060,
      "updated": 1771730060
    },
    {
      "id": "699a748c00000000005a271e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730060,
      "updated": 1771730060
    },
    {
      "id": "699a748c00000000005a271f",
      "text": "[ページ内にあるtagを取得する]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730060,
      "updated": 1771730060
    },
    {
      "id": "699a748c00000000005a2720",
      "text": " ページ内のリンクとタグを見分けて取得したい",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730060,
      "updated": 1771730060
    },
    {
      "id": "699a748c00000000005a2721",
      "text": " APIでページのリンクを取得する",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730060,
      "updated": 1771730060
    },
    {
      "id": "699a748c00000000005a2722",
      "text": "  [/scrapboxlab/Scrapbox REST APIの一覧]の[api/pages/:projectname/:pagetitle]を使う",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730060,
      "updated": 1771730060
    },
    {
      "id": "699a748c00000000005a2723",
      "text": "  そのページ内でリンクされているページが、linksの配列?にある",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730060,
      "updated": 1771730060
    },
    {
      "id": "699a748c00000000005a2724",
      "text": " ページのテキストをリンク名で検索して、リンク名の直前に`#`があるリンクだけを取り出す",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730060,
      "updated": 1771732556
    },
    {
      "id": "699bdbf1000000000055fde2",
      "text": " これだと`#tag`のようにインラインコード内に含まれた`#`つきの文字や、コードブロック中の文字なども拾ってしまいます[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1771822064,
      "updated": 1771822113
    },
    {
      "id": "699bdc08000000000055fde3",
      "text": "  `[https://example.com#tag]`みたいなURLにも引っ掛かる",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1771822088,
      "updated": 1771822112
    },
    {
      "id": "699bdc23000000000055fde4",
      "text": " エッジケース全てに対応するなら、[scrapbox-parser]でhashtagを取り出すのが確実です",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1771822114,
      "updated": 1771822141
    },
    {
      "id": "699a7e4d0000000000221446",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771732558,
      "updated": 1771732558
    },
    {
      "id": "699a748c00000000005a2727",
      "text": "tagがついたページをfetchする",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730060,
      "updated": 1771730060
    },
    {
      "id": "699a748c00000000005a2728",
      "text": " あるタグがついているページをすべて取得したい",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730060,
      "updated": 1771730060
    },
    {
      "id": "699a748c00000000005a2729",
      "text": " リンクとタグを見分けて取得したい",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730060,
      "updated": 1771730060
    },
    {
      "id": "699a748c00000000005a272a",
      "text": " tag(リンク)のページにリンクしてきているページリストを取得し、それぞれのページの情報を取得し、リンク形式で記述されているページは捨ててタグ形式でついているページだけを集める",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730060,
      "updated": 1771730060
    },
    {
      "id": "699a748c00000000005a272b",
      "text": "  tagのページにリンクしているページを取得する",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730060,
      "updated": 1771730060
    },
    {
      "id": "699a748c00000000005a272c",
      "text": "   [/scrapboxlab/Scrapbox REST APIの一覧]の[api/pages/:projectname/:pagetitle]を使ってJSONを取得する",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730060,
      "updated": 1771730060
    },
    {
      "id": "699a748c00000000005a272d",
      "text": "   links1hopには直リンクの関係になるページが入ってる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730060,
      "updated": 1771730060
    },
    {
      "id": "699a748c00000000005a272e",
      "text": "    tagのページ内でリンクしているページと、tagのページにリンクしてきているページ([backlink])が入ってる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730060,
      "updated": 1771730060
    },
    {
      "id": "699a748c00000000005a272f",
      "text": "   linksのページにはtagのページ内でリンクしているページが入ってる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730060,
      "updated": 1771730060
    },
    {
      "id": "699a748c00000000005a2730",
      "text": "   links1hopからlinksのページを取り除くと、tagのページにリンクしてきているページだけを取り出せる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730060,
      "updated": 1771730060
    },
    {
      "id": "699a748c00000000005a2731",
      "text": "  tagのページにリンクしているページのそれぞれについて、情報を取る",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730060,
      "updated": 1771730060
    },
    {
      "id": "699a748c00000000005a2732",
      "text": "   [/scrapboxlab/Scrapbox REST APIの一覧]の[api/pages/:projectname/:pagetitle]を使ってそれぞれのページのJSONを取得する",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730060,
      "updated": 1771730060
    },
    {
      "id": "699a748c00000000005a2733",
      "text": "   それぞれのページ内でリンクがtagになっているかリンクになっているかを判別して、tagになっているページだけを取得する",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1771730060,
      "updated": 1771822052
    },
    {
      "id": "699a748c00000000005a2734",
      "text": "    →[tagがついたページをfetchしたい#699a571c0000000000955c07]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730060,
      "updated": 1771730060
    },
    {
      "id": "699a748c00000000005a2735",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730060,
      "updated": 1771732524
    },
    {
      "id": "699a748c00000000005a2736",
      "text": "堂々と書いたが実際に機能するかわからない [vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730060,
      "updated": 1771732586
    },
    {
      "id": "699a7e64000000000022144f",
      "text": " まだ試したことがない",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771732581,
      "updated": 1771732584
    },
    {
      "id": "699a7e6f0000000000221450",
      "text": " 確かめる機会がない",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771732592,
      "updated": 1771732596
    },
    {
      "id": "699a7e62000000000022144a",
      "text": "  tagとリンクを使い分けていないので試す機会がない",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771732579,
      "updated": 1771732604
    },
    {
      "id": "699a7e62000000000022144c",
      "text": "  ドッグフーディングをしてない",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771732579,
      "updated": 1771732608
    },
    {
      "id": "699a7e980000000000221451",
      "text": " 手順を思いついたのでとにかく書き出しておくことにした",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771732633,
      "updated": 1771732645
    },
    {
      "id": "699a7ea50000000000221453",
      "text": "  あとで自分が利用するかもしれないので",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771732645,
      "updated": 1771732648
    },
    {
      "id": "699a7e62000000000022144e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771732579,
      "updated": 1771732579
    },
    {
      "id": "699a748c00000000005a2737",
      "text": "ページを消されてた",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730060,
      "updated": 1771730060
    },
    {
      "id": "699a748c00000000005a2738",
      "text": " 自己解決されて消したか、諦めたときだと思った[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730060,
      "updated": 1771730060
    },
    {
      "id": "699a748c00000000005a2739",
      "text": " どゆことや[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730060,
      "updated": 1771730060
    },
    {
      "id": "699a749f00000000005a2741",
      "text": " 今朝井戸端を開いたら、[katayama8000.icon]さんがこういうページを書かれてた [vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730079,
      "updated": 1771730391
    },
    {
      "id": "699a749d00000000005a273f",
      "text": "  > [https://gyazo.com/099cc10b21531b65fcda7b74dffae61f]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730078,
      "updated": 1771820840
    },
    {
      "id": "699a74d700000000005a2744",
      "text": "  これができそうな方法が思いついたので、30分後ぐらいに書き込もうとした",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730135,
      "updated": 1771730366
    },
    {
      "id": "699a75be00000000005a274b",
      "text": "  そのときページがなくなっていた",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730366,
      "updated": 1771730370
    },
    {
      "id": "699a756500000000005a2746",
      "text": "  ページが削除されたみたいだった",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730277,
      "updated": 1771732661
    },
    {
      "id": "699a74a200000000005a2742",
      "text": " ページを削除したのはどうしてだろうと思い、",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730082,
      "updated": 1771730791
    },
    {
      "id": "699a758a00000000005a2748",
      "text": "  自分で解決したときとか",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730315,
      "updated": 1771730830
    },
    {
      "id": "699bc184000000000009dcb0",
      "text": "  \t自己解決しました[katayama8000.icon]",
      "userId": "64574844983f38be90afb67e",
      "created": 1771815301,
      "updated": 1771815317
    },
    {
      "id": "699bc296000000000009dcb3",
      "text": "  \t\tkeywardでページを取得",
      "userId": "64574844983f38be90afb67e",
      "created": 1771815575,
      "updated": 1771815590
    },
    {
      "id": "699bc28b000000000009dcb1",
      "text": "  \t\t\t`https://scrapbox.io/api/pages/${projectName}/search/query?q=${keyword}`",
      "userId": "64574844983f38be90afb67e",
      "created": 1771815563,
      "updated": 1771815592
    },
    {
      "id": "699bc51c000000000009dcc9",
      "text": "  \t\t\t\t↑を知らなかった",
      "userId": "64574844983f38be90afb67e",
      "created": 1771816220,
      "updated": 1771816225
    },
    {
      "id": "699bc2a8000000000009dcb4",
      "text": "  \t\tページの中身を見て、欲しいtagでgrep",
      "userId": "64574844983f38be90afb67e",
      "created": 1771815593,
      "updated": 1771815631
    },
    {
      "id": "699bc8d800000000001b3b6f",
      "text": "  \t\t\t`const filterdPages = pages.includes(\"#tag\")`",
      "userId": "64574844983f38be90afb67e",
      "created": 1771817177,
      "updated": 1771817251
    },
    {
      "id": "699bc2e5000000000009dcb6",
      "text": "  \t\t最後にフィルターされたタイトルで再度fetch",
      "userId": "64574844983f38be90afb67e",
      "created": 1771815654,
      "updated": 1771815681
    },
    {
      "id": "699bc4d2000000000009dcc7",
      "text": "  \t\t\t`https://scrapbox.io/api/pages/api/pages/:projectname/search/${title}`",
      "userId": "64574844983f38be90afb67e",
      "created": 1771816147,
      "updated": 1771816204
    },
    {
      "id": "699bc301000000000009dcb7",
      "text": "  \t\t参考PR",
      "userId": "64574844983f38be90afb67e",
      "created": 1771815681,
      "updated": 1771815792
    },
    {
      "id": "699bc370000000000009dcba",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\thttps://github.com/katayama8000/scrapbox-manager/pull/63",
      "userId": "64574844983f38be90afb67e",
      "created": 1771815792,
      "updated": 1771815796
    },
    {
      "id": "699bda20000000000055fddb",
      "text": "\t\t\tその方法はmax100 pagesまでなら有効ですが、それ以上だと限界があります[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1771821600,
      "updated": 1771821622
    },
    {
      "id": "699bda36000000000055fddc",
      "text": "\t\t\t [Cosenseの全文検索]は上限100件までなんですよね……",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1771821622,
      "updated": 1771821638
    },
    {
      "id": "699bdaa5000000000055fddd",
      "text": "\t\t\tなので[tagがついたページをfetchしたい#699af79d0000000000a5b274]が一番確実だと思……っていたんですが、[2 hop search]を使えることに今気づきました",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1771821733,
      "updated": 1771821787
    },
    {
      "id": "699bdadb000000000055fdde",
      "text": "\t\t\t $ await (await fetch(https://scrapbox.io/api/pages/${projectName}/${tag}?search=%23${tag})).json()",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1771821787,
      "updated": 1771821905
    },
    {
      "id": "699bdb52000000000055fddf",
      "text": "\t\t\t これで、`#tag`の形で`tag`にリンクしているページを関連ページリストから得られるはずです",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1771821906,
      "updated": 1771821930
    },
    {
      "id": "699bdb6a000000000055fde0",
      "text": " \t\t\tただ、[2 hop search]に検索上限がないかどうかは未検証です",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1771821930,
      "updated": 1771821952
    },
    {
      "id": "699bdb80000000000055fde1",
      "text": " \t\t\t　もしこちらも検索上限があるなら、やはり[api/pages/:projectname/search/titles]で`tag`にリンクしているページを洗い出して、そこから[scrapbox-parser]にかけて`#tag`が含まれているページのみ抽出するのが無難ということになりますね。",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1771821952,
      "updated": 1771822031
    },
    {
      "id": "699a759600000000005a2749",
      "text": "  諦めたときとか",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730327,
      "updated": 1771730832
    },
    {
      "id": "699a77580000000000221443",
      "text": "  Cosenseの運用方法を変えて迂回できたときに",
      "userId": "64574844983f38be90afb67e",
      "created": 1771730776,
      "updated": 1771817438
    },
    {
      "id": "699a75fa00000000005a274d",
      "text": "  自分はページを消すなあと思った",
      "userId": "64574844983f38be90afb67e",
      "created": 1771817438,
      "updated": 1771817439
    },
    {
      "id": "699bc17d000000000009dcaf",
      "text": "  ",
      "userId": "64574844983f38be90afb67e",
      "created": 1771817440,
      "updated": 1771817441
    },
    {
      "id": "699a748c00000000005a273e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771730060,
      "updated": 1771730060
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7080000000000a5b22e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763465,
      "updated": 1771763465
    },
    {
      "id": "699af79d0000000000a5b274",
      "text": "タグとリンクを使い分けていなければ、[api/pages/:projectname/search/titles]でもよさそう[meganii.icon]",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763614,
      "updated": 1771763954
    },
    {
      "id": "699af87d0000000000a5b275",
      "text": "\ttitleだけでなく、linkが含まれている",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763837,
      "updated": 1771763954
    },
    {
      "id": "699af8910000000000a5b276",
      "text": "\t[2026/02/15#6990e2550000000000b17213]",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763857,
      "updated": 1771763997
    },
    {
      "id": "699af91d0000000000e84452",
      "text": "\t\tたしかに、10000件返ってくることを確認",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763997,
      "updated": 1771764001
    },
    {
      "id": "699af9210000000000e84453",
      "text": "\t\tskipでoffsetを制御するのかと思ったら、Response HeaderのfollowingIdをセットするの知らなかった。",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771764001,
      "updated": 1771764001
    },
    {
      "id": "699af8db0000000000a5b27b",
      "text": "[@cosense/std]を使う練習[meganii.icon]",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763932,
      "updated": 1771763932
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7550000000000a5b273",
      "text": "\t正規表現とジェネレーターは自信なし...",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763542,
      "updated": 1771763556
    },
    {
      "id": "699bdcaa000000000055fde5",
      "text": "\t今なら[Iterator helpers]があるので、`for await`使わずにmethod chainだけで書けるかも？[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1771822250,
      "updated": 1771822275
    },
    {
      "id": "699d927c0000000000f1b454",
      "text": "\t\t調べてみます！[meganii.icon]",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771934332,
      "updated": 1771934335
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7080000000000a5b230",
      "text": "code:main.ts",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763465,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af70e0000000000a5b232",
      "text": " import { pooledMap } from \"@std/async/pool\";",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763470,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b233",
      "text": " import { escape } from \"@std/regexp/escape\";",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b234",
      "text": " import { getLinksStream } from \"@cosense/std/unstable-api/pages/project/search/titles\";",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b235",
      "text": " import { getText } from \"@cosense/std/unstable-api/pages/project/title/text\";",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b236",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b237",
      "text": " const project = \"villagepump\";",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b238",
      "text": " const keywordLink = \"書いてけ\";",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b239",
      "text": " const re = new RegExp(`#${escape(keywordLink)}(?=\\\\s|$|[。、,.!?)\\\\]】）』」])`, \"u\");",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b23a",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b23b",
      "text": " const CONCURRENCY = 5;",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b23c",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b23d",
      "text": " let scanned = 0;",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b23e",
      "text": " let failed = 0;",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b23f",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b240",
      "text": " async function* getFilteredLinks(project: string, keyword: string) {",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b241",
      "text": "   for await (const t of getLinksStream(project)) {",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b242",
      "text": "     if (t.links.includes(keyword)) {",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b243",
      "text": "       yield t;",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b244",
      "text": "     }",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b245",
      "text": "   }",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b246",
      "text": " }",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b247",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b248",
      "text": " const results = [];",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b249",
      "text": " for await (const hit of pooledMap(",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b24a",
      "text": "   CONCURRENCY,",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b24b",
      "text": "   getFilteredLinks(project, keywordLink),",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b24c",
      "text": "   async (item) => {",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b24d",
      "text": "     scanned++;",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b24e",
      "text": "     try {",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b24f",
      "text": "       const res = await getText(project, item.title);",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b250",
      "text": "       if (!res.ok) {",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b251",
      "text": "         failed++;",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b252",
      "text": "         return null;",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b253",
      "text": "       }",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b254",
      "text": "       const text = await res.text();",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b255",
      "text": "       return re.test(text) ? { title: item.title } : null;",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b256",
      "text": "     } catch {",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b257",
      "text": "       failed++;",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b258",
      "text": "       return null;",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b259",
      "text": "     }",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b25a",
      "text": "   }",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b25b",
      "text": " )) {",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b25c",
      "text": "   if (hit) results.push(hit);",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b25d",
      "text": " }",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b25e",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b25f",
      "text": " console.log({",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b260",
      "text": "   project,",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b261",
      "text": "   keywordLink,",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b262",
      "text": "   scanned,",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b263",
      "text": "   matched: results.length,",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b264",
      "text": "   failed,",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b265",
      "text": " });",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7110000000000a5b266",
      "text": " console.log(results);",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763473,
      "updated": 1771763473
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7090000000000a5b231",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763465,
      "updated": 1771763465
    },
    {
      "id": "699af71f0000000000a5b267",
      "text": "code:deno.json",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763487,
      "updated": 1771763491
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7230000000000a5b269",
      "text": " {",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763492,
      "updated": 1771763492
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7240000000000a5b26a",
      "text": "   \"imports\": {",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763492,
      "updated": 1771763492
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7240000000000a5b26b",
      "text": "     \"@cosense/std\": \"jsr:@cosense/std@^0.31.0\",",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763492,
      "updated": 1771763492
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7240000000000a5b26c",
      "text": "     \"@cosense/types\": \"jsr:@cosense/types@^0.11.7\",",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763492,
      "updated": 1771763492
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7240000000000a5b26d",
      "text": "     \"@std/assert\": \"jsr:@std/assert@1\",",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763492,
      "updated": 1771763492
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7240000000000a5b26e",
      "text": "     \"@std/async\": \"jsr:@std/async@^1.2.0\",",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763492,
      "updated": 1771763492
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7240000000000a5b26f",
      "text": "     \"@std/regexp\": \"jsr:@std/regexp@^1.0.1\"",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763492,
      "updated": 1771763492
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7240000000000a5b270",
      "text": "   }",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763492,
      "updated": 1771763492
    },
    {
      "id": "699af7240000000000a5b271",
      "text": " }",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763492,
      "updated": 1771763492
    },
    {
      "id": "699af71f0000000000a5b268",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "649a24da357c4d001c518c25",
      "created": 1771763488,
      "updated": 1771763488
    },
    {
      "id": "699bdcf4000000000055fde6",
      "text": "うまく解決しそうだったので静観していたが、つい口出ししてしまった[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
